Enum Constant Detail

JOBNAME

public static final JobSubmissionProperty JOBNAME
The (grisu-backend unique) name of this job. Defaults to "grisu_job".

APPLICATIONNAME

public static final JobSubmissionProperty APPLICATIONNAME
The name of the application for this job. If you don't want to use mds for this job, specify the value of Constants.GENERIC_APPLICATION_NAME here. Defaults to null.

APPLICATIONVERSION

public static final JobSubmissionProperty APPLICATIONVERSION
The version of the application for this job. If you want the Grisu backend to pick a version, specify the value of Constants.NO_VERSION_INDICATOR_STRING here.

NO_CPUS

public static final JobSubmissionProperty NO_CPUS
The numbers of cpus for this job. If you don't specify FORCE_SINGLE or FORCE_MPI here, the Grisu backend will auto-select a jobtype. Defaults to 1.

FORCE_SINGLE

public static final JobSubmissionProperty FORCE_SINGLE
Forces a "single" type job, even if you specify more than one cpus in NO_CPUS. Defaults to false.

FORCE_MPI

public static final JobSubmissionProperty FORCE_MPI
Forces a "mpi" type job, even if you specify only one cpu in NO_CPUS. Defaults to false

MEMORY_IN_B

public static final JobSubmissionProperty MEMORY_IN_B
The minimum amount of memory that this job needs. Defaults to 0.

EMAIL_ADDRESS

public static final JobSubmissionProperty EMAIL_ADDRESS
The email address to use when specifying EMAIL_ON_START or EMAIL_ON_FINISH.

EMAIL_ON_START

public static final JobSubmissionProperty EMAIL_ON_START
Specifies whether you want an email sent to you after the job started on the cluster. Defaults to false.

EMAIL_ON_FINISH

public static final JobSubmissionProperty EMAIL_ON_FINISH
Specifies whether you want an email sent to you after the job finished on the cluster. Defaults to false.

WALLTIME_IN_MINUTES

public static final JobSubmissionProperty WALLTIME_IN_MINUTES
The walltime of your jobs in minutes. Defaults to 1440 (1 day).

COMMANDLINE

public static final JobSubmissionProperty COMMANDLINE
The commandline to run on the cluster (e.g. "java -version"). The backend will try to figure out which APPLICATIONNAME to set (if you didn't set one) according to the executable you specify here.

STDOUT

public static final JobSubmissionProperty STDOUT
The name of the stdout file. Defaults to stdout.txt.

STDERR

public static final JobSubmissionProperty STDERR
The name of the stderr file. Defaults to stderr.txt.

STDIN

public static final JobSubmissionProperty STDIN
The name of the stdIn file. Defaults to null.

SUBMISSIONLOCATION

public static final JobSubmissionProperty SUBMISSIONLOCATION
The name of the submission location to submit this job to. Use the GrisuRegistry object and it's childs to find one. If you don't specify one, the backend will try to find the best one for you. efaults to null.

INPUT_FILE_URLS

public static final JobSubmissionProperty INPUT_FILE_URLS
A comma seperated list of urls of input files. You can specify local or remote files here. Defaults to null.

MODULES

public static final JobSubmissionProperty MODULES
A comma-seperated list of modules you want to load. This should only be used in if you know what you are doing. Defaults to null.

PBSDEBUG

public static final JobSubmissionProperty PBSDEBUG

HOSTCOUNT

public static final JobSubmissionProperty HOSTCOUNT
The number of hosts to spread the job. Only important for threaded jobs.
